#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:5
msgid "``sort_ascending``: ``enum``, 是否升序排列因子"
msgstr "``sort_ascending``: ``enum``、係数を昇順にソートするかどうか"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:7
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:33 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:33
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:32
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:33
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:32
msgid "``True``: 优先选择因子最小的股票,"
msgstr "``True``: 要素が最も小さい銘柄を優先します。"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingAvgIndicator:9
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:35 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:35
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:34
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:35
